steps.name: Search input details should be entered in searchFlightdetails screen
Click on Search Flights button in searchFlightdetails screen
Search summary module should be displayed as per the search query data
Apply filter result to Emirates carrier in flightSearchResult screen
listing results should be filtered only with the selected carrier in flightSearchResult screen
Select random flight & related price in flightSearchResult screen
the displayed cart price in Cart details page should be aligned with listing price
User should able to enter the travelers details in the details page
